  "remarks": "Considered a fugitive from justice by the Italian authorities and\nsentenced in absentia to 6 years detention on 20 Nov. 2008. Sentenced in Tunisia to 4\nyears imprisonment for terrorist activity and in detention in Tunisia as at Jun. 2009.\nReview pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 20 Jul.\n2009. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
